{"tid":582666,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"呢個世界，既複雜又精密，但又極多缺陷和問題","createTime":"2018-03-06T11:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T12:09:27.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"35c9c4bc1b5936ed8d45097279250011396b4ada","tid":582666,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"無論係自然系統、生態系統、生命、動植物、人體、人腦。或者係人類心理、社會、法律與政治制度、經濟制度、人類建設、電腦系統，都係一樣。<br />\n<br />\n設計非常複雜和精密得黎，又好多問題、漏洞和錯誤。生命世界，彼此合作又彼此競爭，彼此幫助、彼此愛護又彼此攻擊。人類痛苦就係咁樣得來。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪創造者意思，專登比呢個遊戲你玩？"},{"pid":"0d8d9ed235ebe7d5b09bed1b8e22d7e4805cedd5","tid":582666,"uid":155344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:17:13.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會我地都係AI"},{"pid":"bf12696b943f0220b997c7ef3c33e4fb032a705f","tid":582666,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"巴打最近D PO 好有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打試舉出世界有乜缺陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78e6bb989bba867051353c0b7bc106829528a885","tid":582666,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf12696b943f0220b997c7ef3c33e4fb032a705f","tid":582666,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"巴打最近D PO 好有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打試舉出世界有乜缺陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"代答：<br />\n香港法律仲未有全面追溯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/195122_6051a4abc67b5e1f55da6abecf794e1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https