like":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf12696b943f0220b997c7ef3c33e4fb032a705f","tid":582666,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"巴打最近D PO 好有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打試舉出世界有乜缺陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"代答：<br />\n香港法律仲未有全面追溯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/195122_6051a4abc67b5e1f55da6abecf794e1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F195122_6051a4abc67b5e1f55da6abecf794e1a.png&h=38c0f971&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"如果法律沒有限制追溯期，咁我1990年時被虐打，2018年先報案，警方會接受。如果有追溯期，比喻5年，咁我1995年都唔報案，作自動放棄追溯權。<br />\n<br />\n追溯期優點係：人類記憶會失誤，除左會唔記得或記漏野，也有機會記錯野，即錯誤記憶。越長時間，越易錯，誤判機會更高。證據都一樣，時間越長，證據越少。設追溯期可以防止錯判，及鼓勵受害人盡快報警。<br />\n<br />\n沒有追溯期：受害人，除左生理和財物受傷，心理也會受傷。如果我們鼓勵盡快報警，受害人會在調查過程，勾起不幸回憶，遇上先謂的「二次傷害」。為保障受害人法律權益，防止二次傷害，有些法律不設追溯期。任何時間都可以翻案。這可讓受害人心理調適及強壯後，才報案。<br />\n<br />\nPs這個是利與弊討論，不是精密複雜又有缺陷。精密複雜又有缺陷，多見於工程和電腦系統。"},{"pid":"506766cf19fe602188d8cc12b5ff238c4a17a449","tid":582666,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23975a2e3066612f6cd65ba06d88392f4ff35d27","tid":582666,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78e6bb989bba867051353c0b7bc106829528a885","tid":582666,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf12696b943f0220b997c7ef3c33e4fb032a705f","tid":582666,"uid":65023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T11:42:45.000Z","msg":"巴打最近D PO 好有深度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"